    <item>
      <title>中国暗示流动性方在着眼于增长方面存在局限性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-cautions-on-liquidity-party-taking-fuel-off-growth-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向几个月来一直在现金池中游泳的银行家发出了一个意外的提醒，即其流动性增加的目的是振兴经济，而不是帮助支持金融投机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-cautions-on-liquidity-party-taking-fuel-off-growth-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 08:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国收紧IPO，检查上市公司以提振股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-to-tighten-ipos-checks-on-listed-firms-to-boost-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国市场监管机构誓言收紧境内上市要求并加强对上市公司的检查，这是为中国价值 9.2 万亿美元的股市注入信心的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-to-tighten-ipos-checks-on-listed-firms-to-boost-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 08:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
