      <title>拜登的液化天然气冻结推迟项目并危及美国市场份额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/biden-s-lng-freeze-delaying-projects-and-risking-us-market-share</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府暂停向液化天然气出口商颁发新许可证，这已经阻碍了原本计划在本十年晚些时候上线的项目的进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/biden-s-lng-freeze-delaying-projects-and-risking-us-market-share</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 08:01:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本井喷的工资结果可能引发日本央行三月加息的讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/market-players-await-wage-result-key-to-boj-rate-hike-calculus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本最大的工会组织周五宣布了强于预期的年度工资协议，这一结果将加剧人们本已强烈的猜测，即日本央行将于下周自 2007 年以来首次加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/market-players-await-wage-result-key-to-boj-rate-hike-calculus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 23:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本巨额工资上涨后日元走弱：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本最大的工会组织宣布大幅加薪，这可能预示着世界上最后一次负利率最早将于下周结束，导致日元走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 22:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本顶级债券经理预计今年销售又将强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/top-japanese-bond-managers-see-another-strong-year-for-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本顶级债务承销商预计，无论央行在政策上采取什么行动，公司债券和武士债券销售在 4 月份开始的财年中将再次表现强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/top-japanese-bond-managers-see-another-strong-year-for-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
